modName: bain wizard for XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended 2
summary: bain wizard for XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended version 2.xx
descriptionHtml:
wizard.txt for XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended 2.05.

Compatibility
XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended version 2.04, 2.05, 2.06
(untested with other versions, it may work however)

Installation
put the wizard in the main zipped file (so you'll have folder "00 Skeleton Rig", "01 ECE"... and finally the file "wizard.txt" here provided)...

for newbee:
...then open wrye bash, installer tab, right click on the XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended 2.xx, select "Wizard".

IMPORTANT
not all features have been tested. if you see I missed something, let me know, i'll try to fix the issue! bye!
